# Geospatial Time Series Forecaster - Harita Hive AI Tool
# MIT License
#
# ML-based prediction tool for NDVI, rainfall, or land temperature trends
# Uses LSTM and Prophet models for accurate forecasting
#
# Features:
# - LSTM neural networks for complex pattern recognition
# - Prophet for trend and seasonality analysis
# - Multi-variate time series support
# - Uncertainty quantification
# - Automatic hyperparameter tuning
# - Support for irregular time intervals
#
# Supported Variables:
# - NDVI and vegetation indices
# - Temperature (surface and air)
# - Precipitation and moisture
# - Land use change rates
# - Custom environmental variables
#
# Model Types:
# - LSTM: For non-linear patterns
# - Prophet: For strong seasonal patterns
# - ARIMA: For linear trends
# - Ensemble: Combines multiple models
#
# Usage:
# geo-forecaster --input ndvi_timeseries.csv --forecast-periods 12 --model lstm
# geo-forecaster --multivariate temp_precip.csv --uncertainty --export-plots